128
00:13:19,460 --> 00:13:21,539
[SPEAKER_00] Da li je Bob Dylan bio koristan?

129
00:13:21,539 --> 00:13:23,980
[SPEAKER_00] Da li je Jutu bio koristan?

130
00:13:23,980 --> 00:13:24,980
[SPEAKER_00] Kome koristan?

131
00:13:24,980 --> 00:13:26,700
[SPEAKER_00] Da li je bio koristan Ircima?

132
00:13:26,700 --> 00:13:29,120
