133
00:13:29,120 --> 00:13:31,720
[SPEAKER_00] Šta je meni značio Sunday Bloody Sunday?

134
00:13:31,720 --> 00:13:34,000
[SPEAKER_00] Što meni znači Čavoglava?

135
00:13:34,000 --> 00:13:35,700
[SPEAKER_00] Ili što meni znači geni kameni?

136
00:13:35,700 --> 00:13:37,360
[SPEAKER_00] Koja sam ovdje rođena u Zagrebu.

137
00:13:37,360 --> 00:13:39,120
[SPEAKER_00] Mama i tata su mi rođeni u Zagrebu.

138
00:13:39,120 --> 00:13:40,860
[SPEAKER_00] A kad čujem one gene kamene,

139
00:13:40,860 --> 00:13:42,000
[SPEAKER_00] si mislim, to je to.

140
00:13:42,000 --> 00:13:43,279
[SPEAKER_00] To sam ja.

141
00:13:43,279 --> 00:13:44,340
[SPEAKER_00] To smo mi.

142
00:13:44,340 --> 00:13:45,899
