147
00:13:56,240 --> 00:13:57,340
[SPEAKER_00] napadalo, gasilo.

148
00:13:57,340 --> 00:13:58,899
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam bila na njegovom koncertu.

149
00:13:58,899 --> 00:14:01,820
[SPEAKER_00] Tada je moj sin koji je tu sa mnom imao godinu dana.

150
00:14:01,820 --> 00:14:03,960
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam bila na njegovom koncertu na poljudu

151
00:14:03,960 --> 00:14:04,820
[SPEAKER_00] sa tri druga sina.

152
00:14:04,820 --> 00:14:06,419
[SPEAKER_00] Moj muž je bio sa...

153
00:14:06,419 --> 00:14:07,399
[SPEAKER_00] Ili on bio isto sa mama.

154
00:14:07,399 --> 00:14:08,320
[SPEAKER_00] Više se ne sjećam.

155
00:14:08,320 --> 00:14:09,120
[SPEAKER_00] Ja se sjećam.

156
00:14:09,120 --> 00:14:10,700
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam dva dana iza toga letjela

157
00:14:10,700 --> 00:14:11,700
