158
00:14:11,700 --> 00:14:14,720
[SPEAKER_00] I ja čitam izvještaj u novinama.

159
00:14:14,720 --> 00:14:15,700
[SPEAKER_00] I mislim si...

160
00:14:15,700 --> 00:14:17,559
[SPEAKER_00] Pa jesu ovo...

161
00:14:17,559 --> 00:14:19,080
[SPEAKER_00] Jesu ja bila na poljudu?

162
00:14:19,080 --> 00:14:20,679
[SPEAKER_00] Jesu oni bili na poljudu?

163
00:14:20,679 --> 00:14:25,360
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, dvije i sedme sam bila na njegovom koncertu

164
00:14:25,360 --> 00:14:26,220
[SPEAKER_00] na Maksimiru.

165
00:14:26,220 --> 00:14:28,080
[SPEAKER_00] Sa četvero male djece.

166
00:14:28,080 --> 00:14:30,240
[SPEAKER_00] Tada sam bila urednica na Novoj TV.

167
00:14:31,240 --> 00:14:34,519
[SPEAKER_00] I ja drugi dan dolazim na kolegi

168
00:14:34,519 --> 00:14:37,879
[SPEAKER_00] i slušam priče iz novina koje kolege govore.

169
00:14:37,879 --> 00:14:40,019
[SPEAKER_00] Ja kažem, ljudi, pa vi niste bili tamo.

170
00:14:40,019 --> 00:14:43,600
[SPEAKER_00] Meni su se ljudi, meni su se ti opasni muškarci,

171
00:14:43,600 --> 00:14:46,279
[SPEAKER_00] ti kockoglavi, ti divlji, ti svi opasni,

172
00:14:46,279 --> 00:14:48,840
[SPEAKER_00] razmicali da ja mogu s mojim djecom izići sama.

173
00:14:48,840 --> 00:14:52,000
[SPEAKER_00] Izići sama i davali mi prednost da prođem.

174
00:14:52,000 --> 00:14:56,039
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, njega se od 2000. je pokušalo ušutkati

175
00:14:56,039 --> 00:15:00,039
[SPEAKER_00] iz razloga onih što on u nama potiče

176
00:15:00,039 --> 00:15:01,879
[SPEAKER_00] da mi razmišljamo ovo što smo čuli,

177
00:15:01,879 --> 00:15:04,240
[SPEAKER_00] da promišljamo, da sebe sagledamo

178
00:15:04,240 --> 00:15:05,299
[SPEAKER_00] na jedan drugi način.

179
00:15:05,299 --> 00:15:08,120
[SPEAKER_00] I ta politički rat koji protiv njega traje

180
00:15:08,120 --> 00:15:11,000
