187
00:15:21,919 --> 00:15:24,360
[SPEAKER_00] A možeš reći da slušaš svaku cajku?

188
00:15:24,360 --> 00:15:25,700
[SPEAKER_00] To možeš reći.

189
00:15:25,759 --> 00:15:28,019
[SPEAKER_00] To ti je okej, imaš široke poglede.

190
00:15:28,019 --> 00:15:33,860
