193
00:15:38,639 --> 00:15:39,580
[SPEAKER_00] Ovo govori o nama.

194
00:15:39,580 --> 00:15:42,139
[SPEAKER_00] Pa ja sam toliko ispunjena optimizmom

195
00:15:42,139 --> 00:15:43,360
[SPEAKER_00] kad sam vidjela ovo.

196
00:15:43,360 --> 00:15:45,779
[SPEAKER_00] Ovo znači da je pola milijuna ljudi

197
00:15:45,779 --> 00:15:47,460
[SPEAKER_00] u najmanju ruku mu reklo

198
00:15:47,460 --> 00:15:49,299
[SPEAKER_00] Ej, mi te oćemo poduprijeti.

199
00:15:49,299 --> 00:15:50,279
[SPEAKER_00] Ti si nama super.

200
00:15:50,279 --> 00:15:52,779
[SPEAKER_00] Ako pola milijuna ljudi kupi kartu,

201
00:15:52,779 --> 00:15:54,659
[SPEAKER_00] to je dva milijuna ljudi koji kažu

202
00:15:54,659 --> 00:15:56,340
[SPEAKER_00] nama je ovo što on,

203
00:15:56,340 --> 00:15:57,799
[SPEAKER_00] iza čega on stoji,

204
00:15:57,799 --> 00:15:59,179
[SPEAKER_00] što je on i tko je on,

205
00:15:59,179 --> 00:15:59,860
[SPEAKER_00] super.

206
00:15:59,860 --> 00:16:04,240
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da, evo, rekla bi da je njegov doprinos

207
00:16:04,240 --> 00:16:08,600
[SPEAKER_00] sceni, glazbenoj, nacionalnoj, duhovnoj,

208
00:16:08,600 --> 00:16:10,039
[SPEAKER_00] nemjerljiv.

209
00:16:10,039 --> 00:16:13,080
[SPEAKER_00] Da je on takav dar našem cijelom društvu.

210
00:16:13,080 --> 00:16:15,120
[SPEAKER_00] A druga stvar, on je autentičan čovjek.

211
00:16:15,620 --> 00:16:18,659
[SPEAKER_00] On je trebao, samo se trebao čovjeku odreći.

212
00:16:18,659 --> 00:16:21,500
[SPEAKER_00] Samo se trebao odreći te jedne pjesme

213
00:16:21,500 --> 00:16:22,379
[SPEAKER_00] koje su oni tražili.

214
00:16:22,379 --> 00:16:23,240
[SPEAKER_00] I o kojem moram reći,

215
00:16:23,240 --> 00:16:24,320
[SPEAKER_00] moj muž ima tezu.

216
00:16:24,320 --> 00:16:26,879
[SPEAKER_00] Ja se s njim slažem.

217
00:16:26,879 --> 00:16:30,279
