228
00:16:53,720 --> 00:16:54,539
[SPEAKER_00] On je izpreo.

229
00:16:54,539 --> 00:16:56,100
[SPEAKER_00] Loša bila četrdeset peta.

230
00:16:56,100 --> 00:16:57,399
