238
00:17:10,279 --> 00:17:11,619
[SPEAKER_00] Ali mislim da,

239
00:17:11,619 --> 00:17:12,720
[SPEAKER_00] i mislim da ovo,

240
00:17:12,720 --> 00:17:14,440
[SPEAKER_00] što smo čuli o

241
00:17:14,440 --> 00:17:16,619
[SPEAKER_00] premijeru Plenkoviću,

242
00:17:16,619 --> 00:17:18,779
[SPEAKER_00] pa ja mislim da je to njegov veliki poraz.

243
00:17:18,779 --> 00:17:21,079
[SPEAKER_00] Ja mislim da je i da je dobro da je došao.

244
00:17:21,079 --> 00:17:22,259
[SPEAKER_00] Da je dobro da je došao.

245
00:17:22,259 --> 00:17:24,099
[SPEAKER_00] Da je dobro da je došao.

246
00:17:24,619 --> 00:17:29,759
