[SPEAKER_03] bude predsjednik države i tako dalje,

1211
01:03:01,079 --> 01:03:03,760
[SPEAKER_03] pustiti njemu da radi ono što radi najbolje.

1212
01:03:03,760 --> 01:03:05,960
[SPEAKER_03] I to zaista radi vrhunski

1213
01:03:05,960 --> 01:03:08,300
[SPEAKER_03] i trebamo posvijestiti da je on

1214
01:03:08,300 --> 01:03:11,019
[SPEAKER_03] na prvom mjestu vrhunski glazbenik,

1215
01:03:11,019 --> 01:03:13,500
[SPEAKER_03] tekstopisac, kant-autor.

1216
01:03:14,860 --> 01:03:16,960
[SPEAKER_03] Ne bi on okupio pola milijuna ljudi

1217
01:03:16,960 --> 01:03:19,619
[SPEAKER_03] samo zato što je branitelj

1218
01:03:19,619 --> 01:03:21,840
[SPEAKER_03] i zato što piše neke stihove

1219
01:03:21,840 --> 01:03:24,019
[SPEAKER_03] koji možda rezoniraju sa braniteljima.

1220
01:03:24,019 --> 01:03:26,639
[SPEAKER_03] Znači, on je vrhunski glazbenik.

1221
01:03:26,639 --> 01:03:29,400
[SPEAKER_03] A onda još kroz tekstove

1222
01:03:29,400 --> 01:03:33,360
[SPEAKER_03] pogađa bilo naroda,

1223
01:03:33,360 --> 01:03:35,280
[SPEAKER_03] kako prije

1224
01:03:35,280 --> 01:03:37,619
[SPEAKER_03] sa vojnom čavoglave,

1225
01:03:37,619 --> 01:03:38,500
[SPEAKER_03] tako danas.

1226
01:03:38,500 --> 01:03:39,820
[SPEAKER_03] On raste,

1227
01:03:39,820 --> 01:03:41,900
[SPEAKER_03] kako i raste njegova publika,

1228
01:03:42,380 --> 01:03:44,559
[SPEAKER_03] i zapravo je na neki način simbol

1229
01:03:44,559 --> 01:03:46,039
[SPEAKER_03] upravo

1230
01:03:46,039 --> 01:03:48,219
[SPEAKER_03] te recentnosti

1231
01:03:48,219 --> 01:03:49,579
[SPEAKER_03] našeg domovinskog rata.

1232
01:03:49,579 --> 01:03:51,440
[SPEAKER_03] Čula sam negdje na HRT,

1233
01:03:51,440 --> 01:03:52,920
[SPEAKER_03] učini mi se čak da je netko rekao,

1234
01:03:52,920 --> 01:03:54,840
[SPEAKER_03] dolaze i mladi na koncert,

1235
01:03:54,840 --> 01:03:56,699
[SPEAKER_03] nisu to samo teturavi branitelji.

1236
01:03:56,699 --> 01:03:58,780
[SPEAKER_03] Kao da je to bilo,

1237
01:03:58,780 --> 01:04:00,639
[SPEAKER_03] pa i naš gradonačelnik je jednom rekao,

1238
01:04:00,639 --> 01:04:02,300
[SPEAKER_03] domovinski rat je pa se tema.

1239
01:04:03,360 --> 01:04:04,739
[SPEAKER_03] tu vidimo da ne,

1240
01:04:04,739 --> 01:04:05,539
[SPEAKER_03] to je dalje...

1241
01:04:05,539 --> 01:04:06,820
[SPEAKER_03] Da, da, da.

1242
01:04:06,820 --> 01:04:10,280
[SPEAKER_03] Vidimo da je Thompson

1243
01:04:10,280 --> 01:04:12,559
[SPEAKER_03] i dalje mlad čovjek

1244
01:04:12,559 --> 01:04:13,900
[SPEAKER_03] koji je bio u ratu

1245
01:04:13,900 --> 01:04:16,079
[SPEAKER_03] i to i našim mladima daje do znanja.

1246
01:04:16,079 --> 01:04:17,619
[SPEAKER_03] Nije to tako pa se tema,

1247
01:04:17,619 --> 01:04:19,739
[SPEAKER_03] nije to tamo, nekad, negdje bilo,

1248
01:04:19,739 --> 01:04:21,079
[SPEAKER_03] pa se zaboravilo,

1249
01:04:21,079 --> 01:04:23,179
[SPEAKER_03] jer očito se prebrzo zaboravilo.

1250
01:04:23,179 --> 01:04:27,000
[SPEAKER_03] Uglavnom, da se vratim na tvoje pitanje,

1251
01:04:28,500 --> 01:04:31,099
[SPEAKER_03] ipak, budući da čitamo te neke naslove

1252
01:04:31,099 --> 01:04:33,420
[SPEAKER_03] i priče o njemu kao o nekom fiktivnom liku,

1253
01:04:33,420 --> 01:04:34,739
[SPEAKER_03] on je na neki način heroj

1254
01:04:34,739 --> 01:04:39,739
[SPEAKER_03] i simbol tih vrijednosti koje pronosi,

1255
01:04:39,739 --> 01:04:43,139
[SPEAKER_03] ali je na kraju dana ipak i muž,

1256
01:04:43,139 --> 01:04:46,800
[SPEAKER_03] otac, brat, sin.

1257
01:04:46,800 --> 01:04:50,300
[SPEAKER_03] Pokušala bi nekako doprijeti do toga.

1258
01:04:50,300 --> 01:04:52,119
[SPEAKER_03] A evo, poželim i sreću.

1259
01:04:52,119 --> 01:04:54,599
[SPEAKER_04] Sigurno se veselimo o tom poslu.

1260
01:04:54,599 --> 01:04:56,539
[SPEAKER_05] Ako se mogu ja sam ubaciti još prije kraja,

1261
01:04:56,539 --> 01:04:58,719
[SPEAKER_05] samo dva konkreta primjera ovo što sam govorio

1262
01:04:58,719 --> 01:05:01,599
[SPEAKER_05] i što smo svi sad svako iz svoje strane govorio

1263
01:05:01,599 --> 01:05:03,320
[SPEAKER_05] o toj kulturi i nužnosti buđenja,

1264
01:05:03,320 --> 01:05:06,239
[SPEAKER_05] dva samo ovako plastična primjera

1265
01:05:06,239 --> 01:05:07,679
[SPEAKER_05] problematike te današnje

1266
01:05:07,679 --> 01:05:10,079
[SPEAKER_05] i dokaza da problem nije samo u tim strujama

1267
01:05:10,079 --> 01:05:10,980
[SPEAKER_05] koje napadaju danas,

1268
01:05:10,980 --> 01:05:12,940
[SPEAKER_05] nego i nama sami među toj našoj pasivnosti.

1269
01:05:12,940 --> 01:05:14,000
[SPEAKER_05] Dakle, mi smo bili,

1270
01:05:14,000 --> 01:05:16,079
[SPEAKER_05] ja i mladi za domovinu,

1271
01:05:16,079 --> 01:05:17,440
[SPEAKER_05] smo bili nedavno na konferenciji

1272
01:05:17,440 --> 01:05:18,659
[SPEAKER_05] i konzervativnoj Budimpešti.

1273
01:05:18,659 --> 01:05:20,420
[SPEAKER_05] Budimpešte, kao što znamo,

1274
01:05:20,420 --> 01:05:23,440
[SPEAKER_05] puno čvrši bastion konzervativizma,

1275
01:05:23,519 --> 01:05:25,860
[SPEAKER_05] u tom smislu da su puno umreženi

1276
01:05:25,860 --> 01:05:28,760
[SPEAKER_05] i njihove organizacije imaju tamo

1277
01:05:28,760 --> 01:05:30,159
[SPEAKER_05] puno više zamaha nego što imaju tu.

1278
01:05:30,159 --> 01:05:32,519
[SPEAKER_05] Naša je, nažalost, još uvijek većinski se svodi

1279
01:05:32,519 --> 01:05:35,659
[SPEAKER_05] na volontere i takve borbe,

1280
01:05:35,659 --> 01:05:37,340
[SPEAKER_05] još uvijek izajmo reći s katakombi,

1281
01:05:37,340 --> 01:05:37,960
[SPEAKER_05] uvijeto rečeno.

1282
01:05:37,960 --> 01:05:41,400
[SPEAKER_05] Tamo je, dakle, puno jača ta scena.

1283
01:05:41,400 --> 01:05:42,800
[SPEAKER_05] Tamo sam vam pričao,

1284
01:05:42,800 --> 01:05:43,460
[SPEAKER_05] kad smo bili,

1285
01:05:44,099 --> 01:05:46,440
[SPEAKER_05] da postoji niz kafića

1286
01:05:46,440 --> 01:05:48,380
[SPEAKER_05] koji nose naziv po Rogeru Skrutonu.

1287
01:05:48,380 --> 01:05:49,280
[SPEAKER_05] Roger Skruton je, dakle,

1288
01:05:49,280 --> 01:05:50,860
[SPEAKER_05] britanski konzervativni filozof,

1289
01:05:50,860 --> 01:05:52,320
[SPEAKER_05] možda najvažniji konzervativni filozof

1290
01:05:52,320 --> 01:05:53,039
[SPEAKER_05] ovoga stoljeća.

1291
01:05:53,039 --> 01:05:55,500
[SPEAKER_05] Dakle, oni su njega toliko obradili tamo,

1292
01:05:55,500 --> 01:05:57,440
[SPEAKER_05] osim što su mu dali status

1293
01:05:57,440 --> 01:06:00,219
[SPEAKER_05] počasnog rađanja na Budimpešte,

1294
01:06:00,219 --> 01:06:02,079
[SPEAKER_05] nazivaju kafiće po njemu tamo.

1295
01:06:02,079 --> 01:06:03,840
[SPEAKER_05] Mi smo prvu Skrutonovu knjigu

1296
01:06:03,840 --> 01:06:05,579
[SPEAKER_05] 30 godina nakon što Hrvatska postoji

1297
01:06:05,579 --> 01:06:06,559
[SPEAKER_05] preveli 2021.

1298
01:06:06,559 --> 01:06:08,119
[SPEAKER_05] Nakon što je Skruton umro.

1299
01:06:08,119 --> 01:06:09,199
[SPEAKER_05] Prva jedna knjiga

1300
01:06:09,199 --> 01:06:11,519
[SPEAKER_05] od temeljno konzervativnih filozofa

1301
01:06:11,519 --> 01:06:12,199
[SPEAKER_05] ovoga stoljeća.

1302
01:06:12,199 --> 01:06:13,280
[SPEAKER_05] S druge strane,

1303
01:06:13,280 --> 01:06:14,800
[SPEAKER_05] Jungo, o kojem sam pričao,

1304
01:06:14,800 --> 01:06:15,679
[SPEAKER_05] psihoanalitičar,

1305
01:06:15,679 --> 01:06:19,099
[SPEAKER_05] ja, kako sam ga proučavao detaljno,

1306
01:06:19,099 --> 01:06:20,980
[SPEAKER_05] većinu knjiga koje sam njegovih čitao

1307
01:06:20,980 --> 01:06:22,840
[SPEAKER_05] su bile ironično na srpskom,

1308
01:06:22,840 --> 01:06:24,260
[SPEAKER_05] jer naših prijevoda nema.

1309
01:06:24,260 --> 01:06:26,019
[SPEAKER_05] Prvi prijevod koji sam vidio

1310
01:06:26,019 --> 01:06:27,300
[SPEAKER_05] je moj prijatelj Valentino Findrich

1311
01:06:27,300 --> 01:06:29,360
[SPEAKER_05] isto prošle godine napravio.

1312
01:06:29,360 --> 01:06:32,300
[SPEAKER_05] Dakle, te stvari su dio razloga

1313
01:06:32,300 --> 01:06:32,820
[SPEAKER_05] zašto mi,

1314
01:06:32,820 --> 01:06:34,380
[SPEAKER_05] kada nas napadaju

1315
01:06:34,380 --> 01:06:35,860
[SPEAKER_05] i kada napadaju sve te ideje,

1316
01:06:35,860 --> 01:06:37,340
[SPEAKER_05] zašto mi često zapadamo

1317
01:06:38,119 --> 01:06:38,920
[SPEAKER_05] šarane okvire

1318
01:06:38,920 --> 01:06:40,219
[SPEAKER_05] gdje ulazimo zapravo

1319
01:06:40,219 --> 01:06:42,199
[SPEAKER_05] u te boksačke mečeve s njima

1320
01:06:42,199 --> 01:06:43,780
[SPEAKER_05] koji nisu lijepi

1321
01:06:43,780 --> 01:06:45,599
[SPEAKER_05] i koji zapravo na neki način

1322
01:06:45,599 --> 01:06:47,599
[SPEAKER_05] pristajemo se valjati u blatu s njima

1323
01:06:47,599 --> 01:06:48,940
[SPEAKER_05] jer nemamo te temelje

1324
01:06:48,940 --> 01:06:50,619
[SPEAKER_05] jer smo pasivni

1325
01:06:50,619 --> 01:06:51,900
[SPEAKER_05] u toj kulturnoj sferi isto ne.

1326
01:06:51,900 --> 01:06:52,659
[SPEAKER_05] Tako da evo,

1327
01:06:52,659 --> 01:06:53,599
[SPEAKER_05] samo sam ta dva primjera

1328
01:06:53,599 --> 01:06:54,139
[SPEAKER_05] htio navesti.

1329
01:06:54,139 --> 01:06:57,340
[SPEAKER_00] Ja bih rekla da mi nismo pasivni

1330
01:06:57,340 --> 01:06:58,099
[SPEAKER_00] u toj sferi,

1331
01:06:58,099 --> 01:06:59,539
[SPEAKER_00] već da mi nemamo

1332
01:06:59,539 --> 01:07:01,179
[SPEAKER_00] od tuđmanove smrti

1333
01:07:01,179 --> 01:07:02,280
[SPEAKER_00] političko vodstvo

1334
01:07:02,280 --> 01:07:03,639
[SPEAKER_00] koje bi radilo to

1335
01:07:03,639 --> 01:07:05,300
[SPEAKER_00] da ljudi dozne koji je skrutan.

1336
01:07:05,300 --> 01:07:06,960
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, mi nemamo mi

1337
01:07:06,960 --> 01:07:08,820
[SPEAKER_00] ovo djelovanje koje se vidi

1338
01:07:08,820 --> 01:07:09,599
[SPEAKER_00] u Mađarskoj

1339
01:07:09,599 --> 01:07:11,380
[SPEAKER_00] ili ovo što je sada donijela

1340
01:07:11,380 --> 01:07:13,059
[SPEAKER_00] gospođa Meloni u Italiji

1341
01:07:13,059 --> 01:07:15,360
[SPEAKER_00] to je djelovanje kroz institucije.

1342
01:07:15,360 --> 01:07:16,420
[SPEAKER_00] To je kad ti novac

1343
01:07:16,420 --> 01:07:17,539
[SPEAKER_00] od poreznih obveznika

1344
01:07:17,539 --> 01:07:18,199
[SPEAKER_00] koristiš

1345
01:07:18,199 --> 01:07:20,079
[SPEAKER_00] za to da ljudima objašnjavaš

1346
01:07:20,079 --> 01:07:20,880
[SPEAKER_00] što je istina,

1347
01:07:20,880 --> 01:07:21,679
[SPEAKER_00] što je dobro,

1348
01:07:21,679 --> 01:07:23,039
[SPEAKER_00] što je kvalitetno,

1349
01:07:23,039 --> 01:07:23,940
[SPEAKER_00] što oni trebaju znati

1350
01:07:23,940 --> 01:07:24,719
[SPEAKER_00] o svom narodu.

1351
01:07:24,719 --> 01:07:26,340
[SPEAKER_00] Da tumačiš da je brak super,

1352
01:07:26,340 --> 01:07:27,820
[SPEAKER_00] da je divno imati djecu,

1353
01:07:27,820 --> 01:07:28,960
[SPEAKER_00] da te djeca vesele,

1354
01:07:28,960 --> 01:07:30,099
[SPEAKER_00] da nisu samo teret,

1355
01:07:30,099 --> 01:07:31,360
[SPEAKER_00] da napraviš politike

1356
01:07:31,360 --> 01:07:33,039
[SPEAKER_00] koje potiču u obitelj,

1357
01:07:33,099 --> 01:07:33,760
[SPEAKER_00] koje potiču.

1358
01:07:33,760 --> 01:07:35,420
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, mi to nemamo.

1359
01:07:35,420 --> 01:07:37,019
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, mi nemamo politiku

1360
01:07:37,019 --> 01:07:38,179
[SPEAKER_00] koju imaju Mađari

1361
01:07:38,179 --> 01:07:40,539
[SPEAKER_00] i to ne znači da smo mi pasivni.

1362
01:07:40,539 --> 01:07:41,340
[SPEAKER_00] Ja mislim da smo mi odnosu

1363
01:07:41,340 --> 01:07:41,880
[SPEAKER_00] na Mađare,

1364
01:07:41,880 --> 01:07:42,800
[SPEAKER_00] super aktivni.

1365
01:07:42,800 --> 01:07:44,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da Mađari,

1366
01:07:44,000 --> 01:07:45,199
[SPEAKER_00] da se nalaze u ovakvu situaciju

1367
01:07:45,199 --> 01:07:46,260
[SPEAKER_00] kako se mi nalazimo,

1368
01:07:46,260 --> 01:07:48,320
[SPEAKER_00] da pobjediš u domovinskom ratu,

1369
01:07:48,320 --> 01:07:50,739
[SPEAKER_00] da uspiješ krvo ostvariti

1370
01:07:50,739 --> 01:07:51,340
[SPEAKER_00] svoju državu,

1371
01:07:51,340 --> 01:07:52,699
[SPEAKER_00] da bez osvete

1372
01:07:52,699 --> 01:07:53,460
[SPEAKER_00] ideš dalje,

1373
01:07:53,460 --> 01:07:54,219
[SPEAKER_00] orijentiraš se

1374
01:07:54,219 --> 01:07:55,519
[SPEAKER_00] prema budućnosti.

1375
01:07:55,519 --> 01:07:57,079
[SPEAKER_00] Da imaš ovako veliki broj ljudi

1376
01:07:57,079 --> 01:07:58,960
[SPEAKER_00] koji imaju vjeru u Boga,

1377
01:07:58,960 --> 01:08:01,039
[SPEAKER_00] koji poštuju prirodni zakon,

1378
01:08:01,039 --> 01:08:01,619
[SPEAKER_00] koji me osjećaju

1379
01:08:01,619 --> 01:08:02,960
[SPEAKER_00] barem za prirodno dobro

1380
01:08:02,960 --> 01:08:05,199
[SPEAKER_00] i da ti neprekidno te neko gasi,

1381
01:08:05,199 --> 01:08:06,380
[SPEAKER_00] stalno te neko gasi

1382
01:08:06,380 --> 01:08:07,480
[SPEAKER_00] i stalno te neko ruši.

1383
01:08:07,480 --> 01:08:09,340
[SPEAKER_00] A ne damo se srušiti,

1384
01:08:09,340 --> 01:08:10,579
[SPEAKER_00] idemo sutra na koncert.

1385
01:08:10,579 --> 01:08:12,559
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da mislim da,

1386
01:08:12,559 --> 01:08:17,699
[SPEAKER_00] ja sagledavam to da ljudi

1387
01:08:17,699 --> 01:08:19,119
[SPEAKER_00] individualno ne rade dovoljno,

1388
01:08:19,119 --> 01:08:20,159
[SPEAKER_00] ali želim isto tako reći

1389
01:08:20,159 --> 01:08:22,539
[SPEAKER_00] da uvjeti u kojima mi dijelujemo

1390
01:08:22,539 --> 01:08:23,140
[SPEAKER_00] i živimo,

1391
01:08:23,140 --> 01:08:24,460
[SPEAKER_00] svakog od vas

1392
01:08:24,460 --> 01:08:26,500
[SPEAKER_00] neprekidno se obezhrabruje.

1393
01:08:26,500 --> 01:08:27,819
[SPEAKER_00] Aktivno,

1394
01:08:27,819 --> 01:08:30,220
[SPEAKER_00] na puno nivoa vas se obezhrabruje.

1395
01:08:30,220 --> 01:08:31,960
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, vi ne rastete.

1396
01:08:31,960 --> 01:08:34,520
[SPEAKER_00] Mi nismo u poticajnom okruženju.

1397
01:08:34,520 --> 01:08:35,640
[SPEAKER_00] Mi nismo u okruženju

1398
01:08:35,640 --> 01:08:36,220
[SPEAKER_00] koje nama govori

1399
01:08:36,220 --> 01:08:37,020
[SPEAKER_00] daj, odi, odi.

1400
01:08:37,020 --> 01:08:38,319
[SPEAKER_00] Ej, daj, super, naprijed.

1401
01:08:38,319 --> 01:08:39,079
[SPEAKER_00] Pogledaj, ovaj fraric

1402
01:08:39,079 --> 01:08:40,279
[SPEAKER_00] kupio 500.000 ljudi,

1403
01:08:40,279 --> 01:08:41,100
[SPEAKER_00] oni tu mače

1404
01:08:41,100 --> 01:08:42,260
[SPEAKER_00] da će biti velika gužva.

1405
01:08:42,260 --> 01:08:43,340
[SPEAKER_00] Ajme, wow.

1406
01:08:43,340 --> 01:08:44,619
[SPEAKER_00] Gužva će biti,

1407
01:08:44,619 --> 01:08:45,199
[SPEAKER_00] ma nemoj.

1408
01:08:45,199 --> 01:08:46,699
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, to je taj,

1409
01:08:47,199 --> 01:08:48,680
[SPEAKER_00] mi smo stalno u tom ratu

1410
01:08:48,680 --> 01:08:49,560
[SPEAKER_00] da nam se govori

1411
01:08:49,560 --> 01:08:50,859
[SPEAKER_00] da to nema smisla

