[SPEAKER_00] što mi radimo.

1413
01:08:51,760 --> 01:08:53,039
[SPEAKER_00] Nema smisla.

1414
01:08:53,039 --> 01:08:54,640
[SPEAKER_00] Ne isplatiti se to.

1415
01:08:54,640 --> 01:08:55,699
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, tako da,

1416
01:08:55,699 --> 01:08:56,479
