1426
01:09:06,340 --> 01:09:06,819
[SPEAKER_00] Evo tako?

1427
01:09:06,819 --> 01:09:07,840
[SPEAKER_00] Mi trebamo učiti

1428
01:09:07,840 --> 01:09:09,520
[SPEAKER_00] o skrutonu i...

1429
01:09:09,520 --> 01:09:12,100
[SPEAKER_05] Da, da, potis je jako bitan.

1430
01:09:12,100 --> 01:09:12,720
[SPEAKER_05] Mislim da samo ima

1431
