1434
01:09:15,880 --> 01:09:16,819
[SPEAKER_05] Da, da, dobro.

1435
01:09:16,819 --> 01:09:18,420
[SPEAKER_03] Evo, ja bih se samo

1436
01:09:18,420 --> 01:09:19,359
